Emma

No fans – no money

We were supposed to help her generate reach and fans, which worked wonderfully.

Problem:

  • No reach on Instagram, Twitter, TikTok, etc.

  • no idea how to build reach and generate fans

After 4 months with Fandafia:

  • Emma now has a huge reach on social media.

  • We developed strategies for them that work very well

  • new fans are joining onlyfans every day

  • we quickly achieved sales of $37,000

What does Emma Say:

This is my story

I didn’t want to use my private Instagram account for OnlyFans. I didn’t have any other accounts.

Developing a certain reach is extremely difficult because it depends on various factors that you may have no control over. I must confess, I had another agency first. When we did not have success even after weeks, I switched to Fandafia. They helped me build my reach the way I wanted from day one. It was very interesting for me to see that not only my desire to generate fans was fulfilled, but also an income that I didn’t think was possible.

Honestly, can you make a lot of money with OnlyFans? Yes, you can make an incredible amount of money with it. Is it possible to do it all on your own? If you have a clue about all the social media platforms, current trends and marketing approaches, the technical know-how and the many ways to develop yourself, then yes. But that’s too much for one person. I prefer to have a management behind me that I can rely on and without which I would never have gotten this far!

Love to Annemarie!
Without you all this would not have been possible.

- Emma
